# タスクを追加する
###
POST http://localhost/api/task HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "name": "$request->name",
    "grade_id": 1,
    "genre_id": 1,
    "description": "$request->description",
    "is_positive_check": true
}
###

